body_html:
@frap129

Same here.

I'm trying to freeze graph from saved model and get the same error after setting PROTOCOL_BUFFERS_PYTHON_IMPLEMENTATION.

Windows 10
Python 3.5.4
TensorFlow 1.5

EDIT:

Problem solved by using input_saved_model_dir instead of input_graph in freeze_graph.py.
